All Implemented Interfaces:
com.google.gwt.event.shared.HasHandlers, com.google.gwt.user.client.EventListener
public class Link
extends com.google.gwt.user.client.ui.Widget

A standard HTML anchor widget. Use this class to create links to external web pages only. For a link within the GWT application use Hyperlink or use the event mechanism.

CSS Style Rules

  • .cbg-Link { }

Method Detail

setExternalLink

public void setExternalLink(boolean external)
Adds properties to a link to open in the link an external window. This can be used to open a window in case you don't want the user to leave the web application. A use case is to open a help document.

Parameters:
external - If true adds properties to open the link in an new window and removes these properties when false
